# рџљЂ Capstone Automation Framework

This repository contains a **Hybrid Test Automation Framework** built using **Java, Selenium, TestNG, Maven, Rest Assured, and Extent Reports**.
It covers both **UI Automation** and **API Automation** scenarios with a modular, scalable, and reusable design.

рџ”— **GitHub Repository:**
https://github.com/ne20641570/CapstoneFramework

---

# рџ“Њ Project Overview

This Capstone project includes:

## рџ”№ UI Automation (Selenium)

* Automated BSE India website scenarios
* Page Object Model (POM) implementation
* Excel-based data handling
* Dynamic waits & exception handling
* Screenshot capture on failures
* Extent Reporting

## рџ”№ API Automation (Rest Assured)

* CRUD operations for Google Maps APIs
* Reusable request/response handling
* Logging and validation
* Extent Reports integration


---

## рџ”№Database Automation (JDBC + MySQL)

Implements full database validation and CRUD operations using DAO pattern:

вњ” Features Implemented:
* Create table (if not exists)
* Insert user (dynamic test data)
* Read all users
* Read user by username
* Read user by ID
* Update user address
* Patch user phone number
* Delete user
* Random data selection for validation
* Extent logging for every DB operation


# рџЏ—пёЏ Framework Architecture

* **Design Pattern:** Page Object Model (POM)
* **Build Tool:** Maven
* **Test Runner:** TestNG
* **Reporting:** Extent Reports
* **Data Handling:** Excel (Apache POI)
* **Configuration:** Properties file
* **Database:** MySQL (via JDBC)

