# вљ™пёЏ Setup Instructions

## 1пёЏвѓЈ Prerequisites

* Java 8+
* Maven installed
* Chrome browser
* ChromeDriver configured
* MySQL DB setup

---

## 2пёЏвѓЈ Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ne20641570/CapstoneFramework.git
cd CapstoneFramework
```

---

## 3пёЏвѓЈ Install Dependencies

```bash
mvn clean install
```

---

# в–¶пёЏ Running Tests

## рџ”№ Run UI Tests

```bash
mvn test -DsuiteXmlFile=testng-ui.xml
```

## рџ”№ Run API Tests

```bash
mvn test -DsuiteXmlFile=testng-api.xml
```

## рџ”№ Run DB Tests

```bash
mvn test -DsuiteXmlFile=testng-db.xml
```

