# рџЊђ UI Automation Scenarios

### BSE India Website

https://www.bseindia.com/

### вњ” Implemented Flows:

* Login to application
* Navigate to Market Watch
* Capture instruments в†’ Excel
* Group by:

  * Type of Instrument
  * Underlying
* Identify:

  * Highest Notional Turnover per group
* Heat Map Analysis:

  * Gain vs Loss indexes
  * Highest gaining index
  * Highest losing index
  * Indexes gaining > 50 points

---

# рџ”Њ API Automation Scenarios

### Base URL:

```
https://rahulshettyacademy.com
```

### вњ” APIs Covered:

#### 1. Add Place (POST)

* Creates new location
* Extracts `place_id`

#### 2. Get Place (GET)

* Fetches location details

#### 3. Update Place (PUT)

* Updates address

#### 4. Delete Place (DELETE)

* Removes place

