рџ§Є Database Automation Details
рџ“Ѓ Test Class:

UserDbTest.java

вњ” Test Scenarios Covered:
---------------------------------------------------------
Test Case           |   	Description
---------------------------------------------------------
createTable	        |   Creates Users table if not exists
createUser	        |   Inserts user with random data
readAllUsers	    |   Fetch all users
readUserByName	    |   Validate user exists
readUserById	    |   Fetch user using ID
updateUserAddress   |   Update address fields
patchUserPhone	    |   Update only phone number
deleteUser	        |   Delete user from DB
---------------------------------------------------------

